data.Corefile:
.:53 {
    errors
    health
    ready
    kubernetes cluster.local in-addr.arpa ip6.arpa {
      pods insecure
      fallthrough in-addr.arpa ip6.arpa
    }
    rewrite name regex (.*)\.local.gd traefik.traefik.svc.cluster.local
    hosts /etc/coredns/NodeHosts {
      ttl 60
      reload 15s
      fallthrough
    }
    prometheus :9153
    forward . /etc/resolv.conf
    cache 30
    loop
    reload
    loadbalance
}
import /etc/coredns/custom/*.server
